data.description: WELCOME TO BLUE WATER BAY Located just 15 minutes from Destin the famous white sand beaches, This is an amazing place to live. Enjoy the outdoor activities, water sports, hiking, biking, jogging, swimming pools, tennis center, golf and as well close proximity to the marina Lj Schooners restaurant and oyster bar. Remodeled in 2022, waterproof LVP, new carpet, new paint, countertops, each toilets with bidets top and bottom, bluetooth and Alexa were installed in the bathrooms, new electrics switches outlets, HVAC UV sterilizer system and water filter system. Walking distance from the marina. Come to enjoy the most gorgeous sunsets, good music, and great food with your family, and friends.
